I think we should discuss the behaviour of this PR.  @vrothberg and I discussed this in a private IRC, and I think the correct behavior should be:

```
If basename(command[0]) != docker {
             alias docker=podman
             exec command[0] + args
}
if command[0] exists {
     exec command[0] + args
}
exec /proc/self/exe + args
```

